---
title: Indian Beef & Veggie Curry with Jasmine Rice & Crushed Peanuts
description: Rich, creamy and aromatic – this dish has all the elements of your favourite Indian curry! An array of colourful veggies have been cooked in fragrant spices before being mellowed out with coconut milk. Toss through tender beef strips for a protein hit and you’ve got a super-satiating and heart-warming meal.
